URL shortener 

Integrates with the admin, to track the number of clicks on a given IP

Features:

- Exclude URLSHORTENER_EXCLUDE_IPS from the trackiing
- Identify bots and humans :)
- Stats of the clicks


Settings: 

URLSHORTENER_EXCLUDE_IPS - List of ips for avoiding tracking

URLSHORTENER_HISTORICAL - Requires cache enabled

URLSHORTENER_CACHE_KEY -  URLSHORTENER by default